file.name: spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
host: '127.0.0.1:8989'
servers:
  - url: http://127.0.0.1:8989    # The "url: " prefix is required
schemes:
  - http
basePath: /
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: python-swagger-ui test api
  description: python-swagger-ui test api
tags:
  - name: default
    description: default tag

paths:
  /hello/world:
    get:
      summary: output hello world.
      produces:
        - application/text
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          schema:
            example: "Hello World!!!"
      tags:
        - default
